react native nativo 0.78.1 (sin expo)


*****************************************************************************************



configuracion de navegation

instalar libreria de menus (navigation)

npm install @react-navigation/native
npm install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context

****************************************************************



configuracion con kotlin 

editar  Edit MainActivity.kt   

android/app/src/main/java/<your package name>/.

class MainActivity: ReactActivity() {
  // ...

// Agregar esta linea dentro de la class MainActivity

  override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
    super.onCreate(null)
  }
  // ...
}

